title: Hour 1 - Let Russ Sit, 12th-Man Provides Poor Welcome for Russell Wilson
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Let Russ Sit, 12th-Man Provides Poor Welcome for Russell Wilson
description:
Dan reacts to last night Monday Night Football game, questioning the decision by the Broncos to attempt a field goal instead of letting Russell Wilson have a shot, and hw wonders why the Seahawks fans provided such an inhospitable welcome for Wilson's return to Seattle.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
